{
  "stem": "12882.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I must say, and I will say it a little bit more often during this-- during this interview, I must have been born under a lucky star.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The only thing left today is that, when I go downtown, I find a parking place right away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But, otherwise, I am really-- there were so many lucky breaks, it's amazing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well, this was, of course, wonderful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I had everything I wanted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Besides that they were very respected citizens.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was taken to first performances, to gallery openings, to everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was all at the age of 15, without having any-- Besides that, they had a very nice daughter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was another plus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She is now living in Berlin, being married to Ossip Flechtheim, a futurologist at the University in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They returned from America to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They are very, very old and not very healthy people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But I never fail to see them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she is the only survivor of the family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The parents, Factor, and her brother all disappeared, and nobody really knows how and where to.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That was my stay in Prague.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "By one coincident, unlucky coincident, I was assigned to play a concert in Dresden around the beginning of November 1938.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Well, the 9th of November was the Crystal Night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I just had arrived in Dresden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I can't remember any more what date it was and when my concert was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Anyway, my concert would have been in the synagogue or the annex of the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And it never took place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "My father was warned by good-natured, decent Gentile friends that there would be a spontaneous uprising the next night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he should get out of the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the Gestapo came to get him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
